\begin{align*}
D(x)&=\begin{vmatrix}
x+a & x & x\\
x & x+a & x\\
x & x & x+a
\end{vmatrix}
\end{align*}

Expand the first row:

\begin{align*}
D(x)&=(x+a)\begin{vmatrix}
x+a & x\\
x & x+a
\end{vmatrix}-x\begin{vmatrix}
x & x\\
x & x+a
\end{vmatrix}+x\begin{vmatrix}
x & x+a\\
x & x
\end{vmatrix}
\end{align*}

Let's evaluate each minor determinant:

\begin{align*}
D(x)&=(x+a)[(x+a)^2-x^2]-x(x^2+(x+a)x-xa)-x(x^2-xa-xa)\\
&=(x+a)[x^2+2ax+a^2-x^2]-x(x^2+ax)-x(x^2-2ax)\\
&=(x+a)(2ax+a^2)-x^3-x^2-2ax^2+ax^2+a^2x\\
